  "body": "**Problem**:\r\nThe following node modules have different versions in `develop` and `desktop` branches:\r\n - react-native\r\n - react-native-i18n\r\n - react-native-config\r\n - react-native-fs\r\n - react-native-http-bridge\r\n - react-native-webview-bridge\r\n - react-native-keychain\r\n - react-native-securerandom\r\n\r\nIt might be quite complicated to synchronize the versions of those modules, so a simpler approach is needed.\r\n\r\nAlso, re-natal config files `.re-natal` are different across branches.\r\n\r\n**Solution**:\r\nUse a helper script that will configure `package.json` and `.re-natal` depending on the target platform.",
